snippet: The Clemson junior Brianna Rollins broke her own collegiate record in the 100-meter hurdles on the final day of the N.C.A.A. outdoor track and field championships in Eugene, Ore.
abstract: Clemson junior Brianna Rollins breaks her own collegiate record in 100-meter hurdles on final day of NCAA outdoor track and field championships in Eugene, Ore.
